      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure? This car has been so well-loved and is in wonderful shape! It runs like a dream and is perfect for everything from daily commutes to weekend road trips. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it's just waiting for a new home. Come take a look\u2014you\u2019re going to fall in love with how it handles!",
